Titolo: Bomberman Touch

Anno: 2009

Descrizione: Bomberman Touch is a series of Bomberman games for iOS created by Hudson Soft. 
The first game, Bomberman Touch: The Legend of Mystic Bomb was released on July 10, 2008 as a launch title for the App Store. The sequel, Bomberman Touch 2: Volcano Party, released on June 17, 2009. The sequel adds multiplayer and online social interaction through the OpenFeint platform. It was later updated for Game Center support.